# Root .dockerignore — applies to the server build (context = repo root)
# and keeps node_modules / build artifacts / secrets out of every image.

**/node_modules
**/.next
**/dist
**/dist-static
**/out
**/.vite

# Uploaded media (mounted as a volume at runtime instead)
server/uploads

# Secrets — never bake .env into an image (compose injects env at runtime)
**/.env
**/.env.local
**/.env.*.local

# VCS / editor / logs / OS cruft
.git
.gitignore
**/.vscode
**/*.log
**/npm-debug.log*
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# Docker files themselves
**/Dockerfile
docker-compose*.yml
